item.title: About
item.content:encoded:
THE IMPULSE

Despite the endless number of jewelry brands out there, I rarely found something that suited my taste.

Because of this, I’m on a mission to create unique and different jewelry for individuals who refuses to settle - both for men and women.

THE PROCESS

Everything from the initial conceptualizing and designing, sourcing the gemstones, casting and finishing, is made by me.

This makes every piece of jewelry that comes out of the workshop unique, authentic and personally handcrafted with respect for tradition.

THE COLLABORATION

Besides my collection I offer customized jewellery for all ages and genders. Together we will design contemporary jewellery that will make you stand out from the crowd.

Get in touch and lets work together.
